                <h4>Languages</h4>

    
              <p>18-21 credits (two years: 12 credits, or in the case of Arabic, 15 credits) in one language (Arabic, Greek, Hebrew, or Latin) </p>
<p>and</p>
<p>6-9 credits (one year: 6 credits, or in the case of Arabic, 9 credits) in a second language relevant to the program selected from the language lists below.</p>
    
      
      
